00113|January 13, 2010}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=DARRIUS>{{cite news | last = Casadonte | first = Lane | title = Garrett Sets Record For Blocks In Spiders Win | newspaper = [[Chicago Tribune]] | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/topic/wtvr-richmond-umass,0,3963338.story | date = January 14, 2010 | accessdate = June 1, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.richmondspiders.com/sports/m-baskbl/mtt/garrett_darrius00.html | title=Darrius Garrett player profile | publisher=[[University of Richmond]] | work=richmondspiders.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725203424/http://www.richmondspiders.com/sports/m-baskbl/mtt/garrett_darrius00.html | archivedate=July 25, 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n|14\n|style=\"background-color:#FFFF99;\" | {{sortname|David|Robinson|David Robinson (basketball)}}*\n|C\n|{{sort|3|Jr}}\n|[[Navy Midshipmen men's basketball|Navy]]\n|[[UNC Wilmington Seahawks men's basketball|UNC Wilmington]]\n|{{sort|19860104|January 4, 1986}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=COURANT/><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/r/robinda01.html | title=David Robinson | publisher=Sports Reference LLC | work=basketball-reference.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|14\n|{{sortname|Roy|Rogers|dab=basketball}}\n|F\n|{{sort|4|Sr}}\n|[[Alabama Crimson Tide men's basketball|Alabama]]\n|[[Georgia Bulldogs basketball|Georgia]]\n|{{sort|19960210|February 10, 1996}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=DARRIUS/><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/r/rogerro02.html | title=Roy Rogers | publisher=Sports Reference LLC | work=basketball-reference.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|14\n|{{sortname|Loren|Woods}}\n|C\n|{{sort|3|Jr}}\n|[[Arizona Wildcats men's basketball|Arizona]]\n|[[Oregon Ducks men's basketball|Oregon]]\n|{{sort|20000203|February 3, 2000}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/w/woodslo01.html | title=Loren Woods | publisher=Sports Reference LLC | work=basketball-reference.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Rosenbaum | first = Bryan | url= http://wc.arizona.edu/papers/93/91/12_1_m.html | work = [[Arizona Daily Wildcat]] | title= Woods throws block party at McKale | publisher= [[University of Arizona]] | date = February 4, 2000 | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Joel|Anthony}}\n|C\n|{{sort|4|Sr}}\n|[[UNLV Runnin' Rebels basketball|UNLV]]\n|[[TCU Horned Frogs men's basketball|TCU]]\n|{{sort|20070207|February 7, 2007}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=NCAA/><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/a/anthojo01.html | title=Joel Anthony | publisher=Sports Reference LLC | work=basketball-reference.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Keith|Closs}}\n|C\n|{{sort|1|Fr}}\n|[[Central Connecticut State Blue Devils men's basketball|Central Connecticut State]]\n|[[Saint Francis Red Flash men's basketball|Saint Francis (PA)]]\n|{{sort|19941221|December 21, 1994}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=COURANT/><ref name=HICKOK>{{cite web | url=http://www.hickoksports.com/history/ncbaskmgleaders.shtml | title=NCAA Men's Basketball: Single Game Records | publisher=HickokSports.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121206010951/http://www.hickoksports.com/history/ncbaskmgleaders.shtml | archivedate=December 6, 2012 }}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Kyle|Davis|dab=basketball}}\n|C\n|{{sort|1|Fr}}\n|[[Auburn Tigers men's basketball|Auburn]]\n|[[Miami Hurricanes men's basketball|Miami (FL)]]\n|{{sort|20010314|March 14, 2001}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/players/kyle_davis.html | title=Kyle Davis bio | publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc. | work=NBA.com | accessdate=June 1, 2010 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108230816/http://www.nba.com/dleague/players/kyle_davis.html | archivedate=November 8, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Davis | first = Brad | url=http://www.auburneagle.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=417:kyle-davis-a-true-auburn-man&catid=43:auburn-basketball | title=Kyle Davis: A True Auburn Man | publisher=Auburn Eagle | date = April 30, 2010 | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Adrian|Diaz}}\n|F\n|{{sort|3|Jr}}\n|[[FIU Panthers men's basketball|Florida International]]\n|[[UAB Blazers men's basketball|UAB]]\n|{{sort|20150307|March 7, 2015}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=THRU2016/>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|D'or|Fischer}}\n|C/F\n|{{sort|2|So}}\n|[[Northwestern State Demons basketball|Northwestern State]]\n|[[Texas State Bobcats men's basketball|Texas State]]\n|{{sort|20010122|January 22, 2001}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=HICKOK/><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.msnsportsnet.com/profile.cfm?id=100219&sport=mbball | title=D'or Fischer bio | publisher=[[West Virginia University]] | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Deng|Gai}}\n|F\n|{{sort|4|Sr}}\n|[[Fairfield Stags men's basketball|Fairfield]]\n|[[Siena Saints men's basketball|Siena]]\n|{{sort|20050122|January 22, 2005}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=NCAA/><ref>{{cite news | last = Tommelleo | first = Donna | url=http://www.sudantribune.com/spip.php?article7810 | title=From Sudan to Fairfield, Gai chasing NBA dream | work= [[Sudan Tribune]] | date = February 3, 2005 | accessdate=June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n|{{sortname|Mickell|Gladness}} (2)\n|F\n|{{sort|3|Jr}}\n|[[Alabama A&M Bulldogs basketball|Alabama A&M]]\n|[[Prairie View A&M Panthers basketball|Prairie View A&M]]\n|{{sort|20070226|February 26, 2007}}\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{Cite web | title = 2012\u201313 NCAA Men's Basketball Records | work = 2012\u201313 NCAA Men's Basketball Media Guide | publisher = [[National Collegiate Athletic Association]] | date = 2012| url = http://fs.ncaa.org/Docs/stats/m_basketball_RB/2013/2013%2001%20Div.%20I%2010-16.pdf| format = PDF | accessdate